ation. We publish the light curves\nas tables and encourage use of these data by the broader community in\nmulti-wavelength studies and modeling efforts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jul 2021 17:16:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-08"}
