eme\neigenvalue and the maximum eigentuple for sums of random T product tensors,\ne.g., T product tensor Chernoff and T product tensor Bernstein bounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jul 2021 16:18:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Aug 2021 14:21:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
